<DOCNO>36695_1</DOCNO>
<TEXT>1034

</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36695_2</DOCNO>
<TEXT>Year 1034 (MXXXIV) was a common year starting on Tuesday (link will display the full calendar) of the Julian calendar.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36695_3</DOCNO>
