<DOCNO>36696_1</DOCNO>
<TEXT>1073

</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36696_2</DOCNO>
<TEXT>Year 1073 (MLXXIII) was a common year starting on Tuesday (link will display the full calendar) of the Julian calendar.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>36696_3</DOCNO>
<TEXT><onlyinclude>
</TEXT>
